simplesect.para:
All circle parameters are internally handled as CWRUtil::Q5 which means that floating point values are rounded down to a fixed number of binary digits, for example: Circlecircle;
circle.setCircle(1.1f,1.1f,0.9);//Willuse(35/32,35/32,28/32)=(1.09375f,1.09375f,0.875f)
intx,y,r;
circle.getCenter(&amp;x,&amp;y);//Willreturn(1,1)
circle.getRadius(&amp;r);//Willreturn0
.
